Pathology & Laboratory Medicine
Dr. Samir Gupta
M.B.B.S., M.D. (Pathology)
Maulana Azad Medical College, New Delhi

An alumnus of Maulana Azad Medical College, New Delhi, Dr. Samir Gupta has over 25 years of extensive experience in pathology. A well-known and trusted name in Moradabad and nearby areas, he is recognized for his diagnostic accuracy, academic excellence, and ethical practice. With a strong focus on quality standards and patient-centric care, Dr. Gupta has earned the confidence of clinicians and patients alike through his commitment to reliable and timely diagnostic services.

Maulana Azad Medical College, New Delhi

An alumnus of Maulana Azad Medical College, New Delhi, Dr. Kajli Gupta brings over 25 years of rich clinical experience in diagnostic imaging. A well-known and trusted name in Moradabad and the surrounding regions, she is widely respected for her strong academic background, accurate diagnosis, and compassionate approach to patient care. Her commitment to quality, ethics, and patient well-being has earned her the confidence of both patients and referring clinicians.
